    modified_response: "I have successfully integrated the **Natural Tones** design theme into the CO2 Architecture sandbox while preserving all state management, calculations, and local storage persistence.\n\n### Design and Architecture Implementations:\n\n*   **Natural Tones Palette & Aesthetic Card Frames**: Implemented a warm, grounded visual framework with a linen bg (`#f5f5f0`), custom olive highlights (`#5a5a40`), and spacious sage cards.\n*   **Aesthetic Typography Pairing**: Integrated **Cormorant Garamond** for editorial, lightweight italicized display headers paired with **Inter** for clean controls and **Fira Code** for state tags.\n*   **Store Live Simulations**: Added styled, proportional live-action meters and interactive parameters linked to the client-side `store.js` engine. \n*   **Dual Panel Mockup Layout**: Redesigned the output panel as a refined, high-density terminal unit to preview the ES6 store code and manually test custom local persistence callbacks easily."
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
